# Successful Patterns

Document proven solutions, best practices, and effective techniques.

## When to Write

- After successfully solving a complex problem
- When discovering an effective technique
- After implementing a reusable solution
- When establishing a new best practice

## File Naming

`YYYY-MM-DD-descriptive-name.memory.md`

Example: `2025-12-19-mock-primitive-testing-pattern.memory.md`

## Template

See `../../templates/memory.template.md` for the standard format.
